      "representative_excerpt": "I have concerns about this proposed rule. The U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service says the definition has led to inconsistent treatment and an unnecessary regulatory burden. Where? To who? Only vague references to \u201cinconsistent treatment\u201d and \u201cunnecessary regulatory burden\u201d appear in the rule proposal. I am concerned by the lack of any apparent empirical evidence...",
