      "representative_excerpt": "As an individual who, in my professional capacity, works closely with the U.S. squid fishing industry to ensure that the fishery operates in a robust and sustainable manner, I fully support the USFWS proposed rule to revise the definition of shellfish to clearly include squid, octopus, and cuttlefish. This proposed change is long overdue, but very welcome. T...",
